Package: rd
Type: Package
Title: Read files from a directory
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Kittipos Sirivongrungson
Maintainer: Kittipos Sirivongrungson <ki11ip0.s.a.s@gmail.com>
Description: Most file reading function read a single file from file path but not from a directory. 
    This package add capability to your favorite file reading function to read multiple files from a directory.
